<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="relevant-adj">relevant <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'reləvənt/    美 /'reləvənt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>有关的；贴切的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>relevant experience / information
相关经验 / 信息</p></div>

<ul>
<li>(be) relevant to:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The essay isn’t relevant to the topic.
这篇文章与话题无关。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>I don’t think what he said is relevant <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ the topic we are discussing. He has missed the point.  （2015 湖北改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. to  </p></div>